{
  "texts": [
    "RF, like other ensemble classifiers, makes predictions using decision trees.",
    "Choosing the root node at each level of decision tree construction might be difficult.",
    "[62] DT DT is a well-known machine learning technique with several applications in regression and classification issues.",
    "At each level of the DT, picking the root node, also known as 'attribute selection,' is a vital element of the process.",
    "The 'Gini index' and 'information gain' are both well-known attribute selection approaches."
  ]
}